# Google Maps Platform API key with Map Tiles API enabled.
# Required for Google Photorealistic 3D Tiles.
#
# Setup:
# 1. https://console.cloud.google.com/ → create/select a project
# 2. Enable billing (required by Google for Map Tiles / 3D Tiles)
# 3. APIs & Services → Library → enable "Map Tiles API"
# 4. APIs & Services → Credentials → Create API key
# 5. (Recommended) Restrict the key to Map Tiles API + your domains
# 6. Copy this file to .env.local and paste your key:
#
#    cp .env.example .env.local
#
# Never commit real keys. .env.local is gitignored.

NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your_google_maps_api_key_here
